text.tspan: Our Goal is to provision new
infrastructure on our cloud EKS
platform without enabling
production traffic
Team will deploy application and build out infrastructure with Terraform
scripts.
Team will Apply API gateway pattern to establish API version
infrastructure.
Team will validate access to the application
Team will shutdown infrastructure as security is not in place.
Our goal is to deploy lastest
code along with security applied
at the API Layer
Team will leverage CICD pipeline to deploy latest code
Team will enable OAuth security on the API Gateway
Team will make the application communication private and local to the
API Gateway. Then switch out the config for the new API Gateway
Team will enable API throttling at the Gateway layer
Team will have QA do initial testing.
Our goal is to release version
1.0 of API making it generally
available to all consumers.
Team will deploy latest code.
QA will test and sign off
